						<i class="fa-li fa fa-spinner fa-spin"></i><p>Augmind integrates innovative sensor and cutting-edge brain stimulation technology with immersive smartphone virtual reality apps, seamlessly working together, to put your brain at your fingertips.</p>
					</div>
