    <!-- Emotions Section -->
    <section class="content-section text-center" id="products">
        <div class="container-fluid">
			<div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12" id="hum">
					<div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1">
						<img class="img-responsive" src="./images/HumIcon.png"/>				
                    </div>
					<h2 class="productsTitle header">Hum</h2>
                    <p>the Hum uses biofeedback to induce a state of calm.<p>

<p>As you grow more deeply relaxed, a soothing humming sound will grow more audible and shapes will change their colours and patterns, guiding you into a deeper state of relaxation. Breathing exercises will assist this training in emotional regulation. Scientific research has shown this to be an effective treatment for anxiety disorders.</p>			
					
                </div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12" id="deepFocus">
						<div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1">
							<img class="img-responsive" src="./images/DeepfocusIcon.png"/>				
						</div>				
                    <h2 class="productsTitle header">Deep Focus</h2>
                    <p>Deep Focus uses visual neurofeedback to boost concentration.</p>

<p>A flame of a candle illuminates the area. As your focus increases, and your attention is centred, the flame grows in intensity and stabilises, lighting up the surroundings more and more. This instantaneous feedback about what it means to consciously shift and regulate attention, will increase your ability to focus in any situation. Scientific research has shown this to be an effective treatment of ADHD.</p>					
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12" id="flicker">
					<div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1">
						<img class="img-responsive" src="./images/FlickerIcon.png"/>				
                    </div>			
                    <h2 class="productsTitle header">Flicker</h2>
                    <p>Flicker uses light to talk to your brain</p>
                    <p>Depending on the goals you set for yourself in the app, the Neuralink headset will handcraft a highly personalised brain training program, which will utilise high- and low-frequency light stimulation. This has been shown to be effective for cognitive enhancement, such as boosting working memory capacity</p>					
                </div>				
